# Game Concepts Display Order

When editing game concept definitions, the Europedia GUI, or related files, preserve this order (see Ingame_Documentation_Rules.md):

1. All (done)
2. F.A.Q. (todo)
3. Overview (done)
4. Urbanisation (done)
5. Food Production (done)
6. Food Consumption (todo)
7. New Buildings (done)
8. New Trade Goods (done)
9. Farm Capacity (done)
10. Farm Output (done)
11. Variable Harvests (done)
12. Population Growth (done)
13. Population Distribution (done)
14. Other Changes (done — Game Rules, Buildings in Location, Pop Capacity, Prosperity, Devastation, Cheap Food, Expensive Food, Province Current Food Storage, Starvation, AI Changes)

More concepts may be added later. Keep the GUI filter buttons and card layout in sync with this order.

## File naming

Filenames in `main_menu/common/game_concepts/` must match card names (snake_case, pp_ prefix). One file per card.

| Card | File |
|------|------|
| F.A.Q. | pp_faq.txt |
| Overview | pp_overview.txt |
| Urbanisation | pp_urbanisation.txt |
| Food Production | pp_food_production.txt |
| Food Consumption | pp_food_consumption.txt |
| New Buildings | pp_new_buildings.txt |
| New Trade Goods | pp_new_trade_goods.txt |
| Farm Capacity | pp_farm_capacity.txt |
| Farm Output | pp_farm_output.txt |
| Variable Harvests | pp_variable_harvests.txt |
| Population Growth | pp_population_growth.txt |
| Population Distribution | pp_population_distribution.txt |
| Other Changes | other_changes_pp_buildings_in_location.txt, other_changes_pp_prosperity.txt, other_changes_pp_devastation.txt, other_changes_pp_cheap_food.txt, other_changes_pp_expensive_food.txt, other_changes_pp_province_current_food_storage.txt, other_changes_pp_starvation.txt |

Other Changes sub-cards use the `other_changes_` prefix for easy folder navigation.

See Ingame_Documentation_Rules.md for the full mapping.
